<h1>About This Project</h1>

<p>
  This project is a cryptocurrency tracking application built with Ruby on Rails. It fetches and displays real-time data about popular cryptocurrencies, including their prices, market capitalization, volume, and daily changes. The data is sourced from the <strong>CoinRanking API</strong>, which provides accurate and up-to-date information about hundreds of cryptocurrencies.
</p>

<h2>Data Sources</h2>

<p>
  The data used in this application comes from a combination of public APIs and statically generated datasets. Below are the data sources:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <strong>CoinRanking API:</strong> Provides real-time information about popular cryptocurrencies, including prices, market capitalization, volume, and daily changes.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Faker Gem:</strong> Generates random user profiles and transactions for testing purposes, simulating real-world data interactions.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Static Data:</strong> Cryptocurrency exchanges such as Binance and Coinbase are added as static entries, demonstrating a real-world association between exchanges and cryptocurrencies.
  </li>
</ul>